text: Zlatica Mijatović (born 1 March 1922) was a Serbian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Serbian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sombor
